{"tid":2459373,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"點解連登仔唔信有大戶 ？","createTime":"2021-03-24T06:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T06:46:33.000Z","uid":300630,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"35d03fa5a87c71a02a25116a1cf88cdd1a9b5c35","tid":2459373,"uid":300630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T06:35:08.000Z","msg":"現實世界都有有錢人同我地呢啲窮撚啦<br />\n去到股市就冇？<br />\n<br />\n反大戶班傻鳩淨係識話人迷信 跌同升都賴大戶<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">你會唔會係理解錯咗「大戶」呢個term???</span><br />\n<br />\n大戶係唔可能集體做低個大市<br />\n亦都好難逆市控制個股 特別係大股走勢<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">但佢可以係適當時候做適當嘅嘢</span><br />\n至於係乜 你覺得有錢人會share賺錢formula比全世界？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連大戶現實上做到啲乜都分唔清就盲反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果然乎合連登仔風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ef2a91cd6e1a38743e1329adf2d9b95c08e7c4","tid":2459373,"uid":134522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T06:36:22.000Z","msg":"細價股有大戶，但係大市得一個大戶，叫做聯儲局"},{"pid":"bc839a14f45d19ce47011837850c4fd07b254a18","tid":2459373,"uid":300630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38ef2a91cd6e1a38743e1329adf2d9b95c08e7c4","tid":2459373,"uid":134522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T06:36:22.000Z","msg":"細價股有大戶，但係大市得一個大戶，叫做聯儲局"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T06:41:30.000Z","msg":"已經有一個大大隻嘅大戶<br />\n連登仔依然選擇不信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c254418bc31a08a986a0b8bf6e27d4c62af532","tid":2459373,"uid":300630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T06:46:33.000Z","msg":"負皮撚無法接受自己理解以外嘅事物<br />\n默默留下負皮"}]}